# WiFi-ShareFile
a userful tool for share files based WiFi（for android and PC which have  Java runtime environment ）

1.share files between android devices

2.share files between android and PC which have java runtime environment

Usage:

    android: 1. build the project and generate apk
                    2. install the apk to your android device

    PC:           1.copy the two java files from folder named java to your PC
                     2. build the files use java and generate the class files  
                     3.run the WifiClient.class to transmit files to other devices   
                        run the WifiServer.class to receive files from other devices
Note:
  
   In  android devices, you have a easy way to share files  by use  other apps , such as filemanager , which have function of share files
   
   用法：
   
        安卓：1.编译该项目生成apk文件
                      2.安装apk文件
   
        电脑：1.复制java文件夹下的两个java文件到你的电脑
                      2.编译两个java文件，生成class文件
                      3.运行WiffiClient.class文件，向其它设备发送文件
                      4.运行wifiServer.class文件，接收来自其它设备的文件
                      
注意：
    
    在安卓设备上有一个方便的方法发送文件，使用安卓上的文件管理器，或者其它有分享功能的软件，分享文件到该软件，然后发送给其它设备。
